<span style="font-size:smaller;">Last comment by: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/torrence" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1420816); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1420816&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610202746" alt="Torrence" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1420816)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/torrence" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1420816); return false;">Torrence</a></span>, <span class="odate time_1590662349 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">28 May 2020 10:39</span></span><br />
<em><span style="font-size:.75em;">appliance auditory cognitohazard electronic empathic mind-affecting safe scp</span></em></p>

    
    
    
    </div>
<hr />
<blockquote>
<p>She laughs a moment later, but the crumbling remains in your mind to this day, deep in the pit of your coward's stomach. This is you.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>A meditation on identity and vicarious experience.</p>
