<p>Now, here are some <strong>favorite SCPs</strong> of mine (that I didn't write):</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;In&nbsp;no&nbsp;particular&nbsp;order....</a></div>
