<hr />
<p>This was really the SCP that got me formally &quot;into&quot; the website; though I'd read SCPs prior to this one, I re-found the website through a link to 3008 on the website MetaFilter. That was just a couple of years ago; I'd pop back in every now and then to read from that point, until late 2019 when I finally decided to see about the folks who write this crazy shit.</p>
